long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Big update! Reconfigured the API to get rid of cold starts. What does this mean? Faster alt text generation! Completely redesigned the UI and fixed common bugs! 

You can now edit alt text both in the Webflow media library as well as in the image settings in the Webflow Designer!

Thank you to everyone who has been using this tool, we hope to continue improving it to help further speed up your Webflow workflow!
